#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.103:4.1"
msgid "1.103. Bandhurattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.103. Bandhura"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc103"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts103"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.103:5.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ etena atthiko,"
msgstr "I don’t need this—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.103:5.2"
msgid "Sukhito dhammarasena tappito;"
msgstr "I’m happy and satisfied with the sweet teaching."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.103:5.3"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"var\" title=\"pitvāna (bj, s2, s3, pts2) | pītvāna (pts1)\" id="
"\"note72\">Pitvā</span> rasaggamuttamaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ve drunk the best, the supreme nectar:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.103:5.4"
msgid "Na ca kāhāmi visena santhavan”ti."
msgstr "I won’t go near poison."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
